Package: straindys
Type: Package
Title: A collection of tools to calculate different strain and dyssynchrony metrcis for CMR FT
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Loewenstein", email = "loewenstein.daniel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A grewing collection of tools to help faciliatate calculation of newly
    developed strain and dyssynchrony metrics. Tools both for global dyssynchrony
    as well as regional. Built for use with CMR FT, and the Medviso Segment software.
